<div class="page-wrapper" data-section-type="skin-test-section">
  <div class="about-head-wrapper">
    <div class="page-width">
      <div class="sktest-header-text-container">
        <h1 class="mobile-h1">{{page.title}}</h1>
        <p> 
        {{page.content}}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="small-container res-hide" id="sktest-res">
      <h1 id="sktest-res-header" class="mobile-h1"> </h1>
      <p id="sktest-res-text" class="m-top-8"> </p>
      <p id="sktest-res-text-sol" class="m-top-16"> </p>
      <p id="sktest-res-sensitive" class="m-top-16"> </p>
    </div>
    <div class="sktest-container" id="sktest" display="none">
      <form class="sktestForm">
        <p class="sktest-warning-text" id="sktest-not-filled">Choosen an option for each question</p>

        <p>1. How would you describe you pores?</p>
          <div class="sktest-input">
            <label><input type="radio" name="pore-size" value="big"> Very visible</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="pore-size" value="normal"> Medium size</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="pore-size" value="small"> Not so visible</label>
          </div>

        <p>2. On what areas to you feel dry?</p>
          <div class="sktest-input">            
            <label><input type="radio" name="dry-spots" value="whole"> Whole face</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="dry-spots" value="u-zone"> Cheeks and jawbone </label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="dry-spots" value="none"> None</label>
          </div>

        <p>3. On what areas to you feel oily?</p>
          <div class="sktest-input">
            <label><input type="radio" name="oil-spots" value="whole"> Whole face</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="oil-spots" value="none"> None</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="oil-spots" value="t-zone"> Forehead, nose and chin</label>
          </div>

        <p>4. Does your face feel itchy?</p>
          <div class="sktest-input">
            <label><input type="radio" name="itchy" value="much"> Very much</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="itchy" value="small"> Little</label><br>
            <label><input type="radio" name="itchy" value="none"> None</label>
          </div>


          <button type="submit">Show Results</button>
      </form>
    <div>
  </div>
</div>